message:
History:  laptop came in heavily water damaged.  ssd got shorted out so i replaced the board about 6 months ago.  this replacement board lasted 6 months and came back no power.

820-01700
i get 20v and drawing .45-.117amps then resets.

i checked ppbus - 12.6v
Is the machine recognized in DFU?
i connected board to another mac with apple configurator.  nothing popped up.  i also tried putting board back in housing and followed the dfu process and nothing popped up.

Of course, try to enter into DFU.
Check if voltages go stable then.
